349
00:21:15.666 --> 00:21:16.832
Good luck.

350
00:21:18.708 --> 00:21:21.125
<i>Please make your way
to the conference room.</i>

351
00:21:26.208 --> 00:21:29.142
Hi. sweetheart.
They're about to start. shall we sit?

352
00:21:29.166 --> 00:21:30.457
-Yeah. Yeah.
-Yeah?

